Burkhalter May Increase Profit, Confirms Outlook, CEO Tells F&W

-- B y   G i l e s   B r o o m
-- 
2011-07-26T16:46:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-26/burkhalter-may-increase-profit-confirms-outlook-ceo-tells-f-w.html
Burkhalter Holding AG (BRKN)  may increase
its earnings-per-share when it reports on Sept. 6,  Finanz und
Wirtschaft  said in a pre-release, citing an interview with Chief
Executive Officer Marco Syfrig to be published tomorrow.  Burkhalter has a “positive” outlook and is “constantly
in discussions” to acquire smaller electrical installation
companies, Finanz quoted Syfrig as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Giles Broom in Zurich at 
 gbroom@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly in Paris at 
 fconnelly@bloomberg.net  